snippet.title: SpongeBob SquarePants™: Diner Dash (PC) - Full Game HD Walkthrough - No Commentary
snippet.description:
The old PC version, NOT the mobile version! Includes all 50 levels with an EXPERT score, in 1080p60, recorded with Elgato HD60, without commentary.

If you enjoyed watching this video, please leave a like and subscribe! I would very much appreciate it!

Diner Dash was a huge part of my youth and so I have always planned on uploading gameplay to my channel. I have also played this game, the SpongeBob version, as a kid. This game can be fairly difficult at times, especially getting the expert scores. Enjoy!

Story: SpongeBob Diner Dash is a casual time management game where you control SpongeBob as he serves food in Mr. Krab's Krusty Krab restaurant.

Your objective is to serve all of your customers on time and with good service, including serving snacks in time, the right table and a possible expert score.

- Single Player
- Seat customers quickly, keep them fed, and watch the tips and profits roll in
- Grow your restaurants through 5 complete renovations; 50 challenging levels
- 5 different types of customers, each behaving uniquely
- Fast-paced puzzles; 2 modes of play--Career and Endless Shift

Release Dates - May 11, 2006
Genre - Time Management, Casual
Platforms - Windows (different version for iOS and Android)
Developer - PlayFirst, Snap2Play
Publisher - NickArcade, PlayFirst

My Xbox gamertag: TGG Yari
My PlayStation gamertag: ToughGamingGuyYT
My Steam: toughgamingguy2

Wanna see more of my fantastic walkthroughs? Give it a go: https://www.youtube.com/user/ToughGamingGuy/playlists
